sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Siswa
    participant UI as Peringkat View
    participant Ctrl as PeringkatController
    participant Rank as ScoresAndRanking Model
    participant Pivot as Pivot (classroom_user)

    Siswa->>UI: Akses Halaman Peringkat (Ubah Tab Filter)
    UI->>Ctrl: GET /peringkat/{type}/{id?}
    
    alt type == 'global'
        Ctrl->>Rank: with('user')->orderByDesc('total_xp')->get()
    else type == 'kelas'
        Ctrl->>Rank: whereHas('user.classrooms', id)->orderByDesc('total_xp')
        Rank->>Pivot: INNER JOIN data kelas user
    end
    
    Rank-->>Ctrl: Collection Siswa Tertinggi
    
    note right of Ctrl: Hitung ranking relatif (1, 2, 3...) & cari posisi user saat ini
    
    Ctrl-->>UI: Render View (peringkat.index) dengan data $leaderboard
    UI-->>Siswa: Tampilkan Tabel Hall of Fame